1] Install Bootstrap
cmd---> npm install bootstrap --save

2] For Bitcoin Chart Install Chart.js
cmd---> npm install angular2-chartjs 
for Modification of chart, Please Check chart.js library

3] Below are the API used for real time data of cryptocurrency
  i] [https://api.coinmarketcap.com/v2/global/]  for Bitcoin market capital in real time
 ii] [https://api.coinmarketcap.com/v1/ticker/]  for getting all crypto prices in real time
iii] [https://api.blockchain.info/charts/market-price?cors=true&format=json&lang=en] for bitcoin chart

4] Also add the rxjs in project
cmd ---> npm install --save rxjs-compat
